  </li>
  
  <li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px;">
    <a href="https://www.indeed.com/jobs?q=agile&amp;l=Boston,+MA&amp;radius=25&amp;sort=date" style="color: #d52a33;" target="_blank"><b>agile</b></a>&nbsp;<b>***</b> | 5,169 <span style="color: green;"><b>UP 9%</b></span>
  </li>

  <li style="margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; padding: 0px;">
